command: ping (ping skeniranje preveri online status hosta -- nmap -sP [hostname])
port (TCP scan FTP(21), SSH(22), SMTP(25), HTTP(80), POP(110), IMAP(143), HTTPS(443), SMB(445) -- nmap -sV -p 21,22,25,80,110,143,443,445 [hostname]
